NUMBER 1232
NAME Rat's Nest
CAVE
PARTIAL_DARKNESS
REGION 15
CHANNEL 68
CALL 69
MINEA
*DESCRIPTION_START
Oddly, after the awkward crawl inside, the interior of the chamber seems
quite spacious. Truly enormous piles of dry leaves and bits of cloth form
numerous rodent nests. Some of the occupants stare out from their beds
suspiciously, not quite sure they want to attack yet. The worst part, other
than the odor, is that either the rats have gotten a lot bigger... or
someone else has gotten smaller.
*DESCRIPTION_END
