; wide darkened opening (back out to Whispering Trees)
ITEM 1 468 ADJ1=717 ADJ2=481
; gargantuan rat nest
ITEM 2 438 ADJ1=451 ADJ2=559
; enormous shadow rat
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 1
Imagine a typical rat's nest: tatters of scavenged cloth, fragments of
leaves, and pieces of straw all gnawed up into little bits and jumbled
together into a soft, if somewhat aromatic, heap. Now imagine said nest
about a hundred times normal size.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 2
Seen up this close, not to mention at such a magnified view, even this very
young rat is an intimidating sight. Long whiskers twitch as it gazes back in
a mixture of curiosity, puzzlement, and defensive hostility.
*DESCRIPTION_END
