NUMBER 1233
NAME Burial Chamber
CAVE
DARKNESS
REGION 15
CHANNEL 68
MONSTER_GROUP 36
CALL 69
MINEA
*DESCRIPTION_START
A nearly empty round chamber greets the eye. The slightest movement stirs
up great clouds of dust, tiny golden motes that drift through the dim light.
Whatever treasure might have been buried down here has long since decayed
away into nothingness. Strange, then, that the desiccated body resting upon
its stone slab is still intact. Any death stench has long since faded, yet a
sense of lingering corruption permeates the musty air.
*DESCRIPTION_END
