*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 1
Necromantic glyphs have been carved all along the four vertical sides, ringing
the corpse within a circle of dark preservative magic. Even the dust of untold
years cannot erase the sense of malevolent power held inside this structure.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 2
