what race is difficult to discern. His arms are folded across his chest in the
traditional repose of the dead, yet the entire body is far less dusty than the
rest of the chamber. Perhaps it is a trick of the light, but a faint sickly
green glow seems to emanate from within the empty ribcage.
*DESCRIPTION_END
