      CLEARVERB 
         EQUAL JABITEMVAL1 ITEMVAL1
         EQUAL JABITEMVAL2 ITEMVAL2
         EQUAL JABITEMVAL3 ITEMVAL3          
         EQUAL JABITEMVAL4 ITEMVAL4
         EQUAL JABITEMVAL5 ITEMVAL5
         RANDOM DUMMY1 1 25 0
         SETITEMADJ -1 1 JABADJ1
         SETITEMVAL -1 1 JABITEMVAL1
         SETITEMVAL -1 2 JABITEMVAL2
         SETITEMVAL -1 3 JABITEMVAL3
         SETITEMVAL -1 4 JABITEMVAL4
         SETITEMVAL -1 5 JABITEMVAL5
      ECHO PLAYER After the item has been in the liquid for a bit, Korrvuz fishes it out and hands it to you.
