NUMBER 1235
NAME Submerged Chamber
UNDERSEA
DARKNESS
REGION 15
CHANNEL 68
*DESCRIPTION_START
This chamber is larger than it first appeared, and although the ceiling
is low, there is room for several people inside, waist deep in the cold
water. Long, slender plants sway in the gentle current. The subterranean
stream that flows into the lake has its source near here. A basalt ledge
has worn away into a dome overhead, where bubbles swept in by the water
have collected to form a large pocket of fresh air.
*DESCRIPTION_END
