; long slender water plant
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 0
Glittering black sand marks the distant edge of the curved shoreline. The
waves lap against it in an eternal rhythm, barely visible from the chamber.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 1
Light makes swirling patterns on the surface of the water, which are
mirrored on the wet black stone in a dappled shimmer. Delicate skeletons
of fossilized fish are imbedded here and there in the rock. Amidst the
moving reflections, they seem to swim - phantom fish in ghostly water.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 2
The stems are long and supple, held upright by the water in which the
plant lives. It has long, delicate leaves that are almost white in color,
with only the barest tint of green.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFENTRY -1
   PLREVENT 1
