*DESCRIPTION_START
Heralded by a cacophony of hideous screeching, this creature sounds like a
devilish army all its own as it approaches. Its fanged maw gapes wide in
constant screams of torment even as it strides powerfully into battle. Fur
and scales, lank hair and leathery wings combine into a uniquely nightmarish
image. But most grotesque are the twisted, evil faces imbedded in the slick
flesh of its abdomen, that snarl and spit at foes with a life of their own.
